Package: jiopc-session-hibernate
Version: 0.1.0
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Team JioPC-IIT Bombay <ayush04-c@github.com>
Depends: python3 (>= 3.10), python3-yaml, wmctrl, zenity, libnotify-bin, xdotool
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Description: Cross-VM session hibernate and restore for JioPC
 Automatically captures all running GUI application state when a user
 disconnects from a JioPC virtual machine, and restores it on next login
 regardless of which VM in the pool the user is assigned to.
